A HexAstral satellite app — generated by `bun gen satellite`.

## Status

v0.1.0 scaffold. Manual setup required:

1. `cd apps/{{slug}}-app && eas init` — fills `EAS_PROJECT_ID`
2. Paste the project ID into `app.json` (`extra.eas.projectId`) and the
   four `EXPO_PUBLIC_EAS_PROJECT_ID` slots in `eas.json`
3. Apple Developer → Identifiers → register `com.hexastral.{{bundleSuffix}}`
4. App Store Connect → create app
5. RevenueCat → create products `{{slug}}_pro_monthly` and `{{slug}}_pro_annual`
6. Designer → `assets/icon.png` and `assets/splash.png`

